description: Fantastic opportunity to own this well maintained East Side two family home. Unit two is the owners bi-level unit offering a large fully appliance eat -in-kitchen, which walks out to a spacious private deck with patio access. This level includes an open living room, small office space, 1/2  bath and laundry. The upstairs has two large bedrooms and full bath. One bedroom has a walk in closet and the other has a huge built -in closet. Hardwood floors and central air conditioning throughout. Lower duplex has an open floor plan on the first floor level with a bright open living living room area. A Half bath with laundry is also on this level. Private deck off the kitchen w fenced in patio area. The lower level has two good sized bedrooms with a full bath. Great opportunity for an investor or owner occupant. Great loc. only two blocks from popular beaches, and close to shops, restaurants and bars. Bus to downtown, Copley, seaport and redline. Easy access to highways.
